sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client
  participant GW as API Gateway
  participant RL as Rate Limiter
  participant R as Redis
  participant APP as App Service

  C->>GW: HTTP request
  GW->>RL: isRequestAllowed(clientId, ruleId)
  RL->>R: Lua script (refill + decrement)
  R-->>RL: allowed, remaining, resetTime
  alt allowed
    RL-->>GW: OK + headers
    GW->>APP: forward request
    APP-->>C: 200 response
  else denied
    RL-->>GW: reject
    GW-->>C: 429 Too Many Requests
  end
